      "description": "Well-kept older car in good overall condition that runs and drives well and should make a solid daily driver. It presents nicely for its age, with a clean overall appearance, a tidy interior, and only the kind of light cosmetic wear and small imperfections you\u2019d expect from normal use. Everything about it feels like a good, honest vehicle that has been used but not abused. If you want something clearly nicer than a fair-condition driver without paying mint-condition money, this is a strong option.",
